    <!--
        Plugin logo, converted from the crest SVG in
        BrandingPackage/01 Logo (dark backgrounds)/02 Crest Icon/SVG/pa-crest-gold-master-icon.svg
        (viewBox 278x257). The crest is seven pieces: an outer ring, the center trophy, and five
        surrounding badges. Each geometry key holds one SVG path; PlayAch.Image.Logo redraws them
        with the master gradients (LinearGradientBrush MappingMode="Absolute", Start/EndPoint taken
        from each SVG userSpaceOnUse gradient's x1,y1/x2,y2).

        Alignment: the trophy center (x 138.141, y 144.300) sits ~16 units below the crest bounds
        center, so a naive image would render the trophy low relative to vertically-centered text.
        The final transparent GeometryDrawing pads the DrawingImage bounds to a box symmetric about
        the trophy center (Rect 2.566,0,271.150,288.6: left = 2*138.141-273.716, bottom = 2*144.300),
        so every <Image VerticalAlignment="Center"> centers the trophy on the adjacent text midline.
        The visible crest is then 256.5/288.6 of the image height; usage sites size up accordingly.

        PlayAch.Geometry.TrophyIcon is the flat trophy silhouette (from
        BrandingPackage/01 Logo (dark backgrounds)/01 Trophy Icon/SVG/pa-trophy-flat-white-icon.svg,
        viewBox 181x169), used by the sidebar/top-panel icons which supply their own foreground brush.
    -->

